## 🔌 **API 映射具体实例**

### 1. 生命周期映射示例

#### Android 代码
```java
public class MainActivity extends AppCompatActivity {

    private TextClock textClock;
    private Button refreshButton;

    @Override
    protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
        super.onCreate(savedInstanceState);
        setContentView(R.layout.activity_main);

        textClock = findViewById(R.id.text_clock);
        refreshButton = findViewById(R.id.refresh_button);

        refreshButton.setOnClickListener(v -> {
            // 刷新逻辑
        });
    }

    @Override
    protected void onResume() {
        super.onResume();
        startTimeUpdates();
    }

    @Override
    protected void onPause() {
        super.onPause();
        stopTimeUpdates();
    }

    private void startTimeUpdates() {
        // 启动定时器
    }

    private void stopTimeUpdates() {
        // 停止定时器
    }
}
```

#### HarmonyOS 映射代码
```typescript
@Entry
@Component
struct MainPage {
    @State textClockValue: string = '';
    @State timerHandle: number = 0;

    build() {
        Column() {
            Text(this.textClockValue)
                .fontSize(48)

            Button('Refresh')
                .onClick(() => this.onRefreshClicked())
        }
    }

    onPageShow() {
        // 映射: onCreate() + onResume()
        this.initializeUI();      // 初始化 UI (类似 onCreate)
        this.startTimeUpdates();  // 启动更新 (类似 onResume)
    }

    onPageHide() {
        // 映射: onPause()
        this.stopTimeUpdates();   // 停止更新 (类似 onPause)
    }

    private initializeUI() {
        // 获取初始值
        this.updateTextClock();
    }

    private onRefreshClicked() {
        // 映射: button.setOnClickListener()
        this.updateTextClock();
    }

    private startTimeUpdates() {
        // 启动定时器 (HarmonyOS 特有)
        this.timerHandle = setInterval(() => {
            this.updateTextClock();
        }, 1000);
    }

    private stopTimeUpdates() {
        // 停止定时器
        if (this.timerHandle) {
            clearInterval(this.timerHandle);
        }
    }

    private updateTextClock() {
        // 映射: TextView.setText()
        this.textClockValue = new Date().toLocaleTimeString();
    }
}
```

